Terminator还支持自定义快捷键，字体和颜色配置，使用户可以根据自己的需求进行个性化的定制。</p>
<h2 id="安装">安装</h2>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>apt <span class="nb">install </span>terminator
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="将terminator设定为默认终端">将Terminator设定为默认终端</h2>
<p>设定后的好处就是可以通过<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ctrl+alt+t</code>直接调出Terminator画面。</p>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nb">sudo </span>update-alternative <span class="nt">--config</span> x-terminal-emulator
</code></pre></div></div>

